                            'Batonnade'  V1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Batonnade' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where the idea is to place bars
to create alignments of 8 sets of horizontal bars in the rows or 8
sets of vertical bars in the columns. Each set of bars from any
series must have one bar more or less than the number of bars on
either side in the series.

  The more bars there are in a series, the higher the number of
points you will get...

  Have fun!

